<tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>805</anchor> <rss>erct-003I.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Corollary</taxon> <addr>erct-003I</addr>  <route>erct-003I.xml</route> <date><year>2024</year> <month>2</month> <day>10</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title><link href="erct-000V.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000V" title="Equivalence of types">Equivalence</link> between <link href="erct-000V.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000V" title="Equivalence of types">equivalences</link> and <link href="erct-003F.xml" type="local" addr="erct-003F" title="Bijection">bijections</link></title>  <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-003I.agda" type="external">erct-003I.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>The correspondence between <link href="erct-000U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000U" title="Biinverse">biinvertible</link> and <link href="erct-003F.xml" type="local" addr="erct-003F" title="Bijection">bijective</link> maps of <ref addr="erct-003H" href="erct-003H.xml" taxon="Corollary"/> and <ref addr="erct-002Z" href="erct-002Z.xml" taxon="Corollary"/> lifts to an <link href="erct-000V.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000V" title="Equivalence of types">equivalence</link> from the type of <link href="erct-000V.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000V" title="Equivalence of types">equivalences</link> to the type of <link href="erct-003F.xml" type="local" addr="erct-003F" title="Bijection">bijections</link>.</p>
 
   
   <tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="false" numbered="true" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>806</anchor>  <taxon>Proof</taxon>    <date><year>2024</year> <month>2</month> <day>10</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors>   </frontmatter> <mainmatter>
 <p>By <ref addr="erct-003G" href="erct-003G.xml" taxon="Corollary"/> and <ref addr="erct-002S" href="erct-002S.xml" taxon="Corollary"/> via <ref addr="erct-003D" href="erct-003D.xml" taxon="Definition"/>.</p>
</mainmatter> </tree>
 
</mainmatter> <backmatter><contributions/> <context/> <related><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>807</anchor> <rss>erct-003H.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Corollary</taxon> <addr>erct-003H</addr>  <route>erct-003H.xml</route> <date><year>2024</year> <month>2</month> <day>10</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title><link href="erct-000U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000U" title="Biinverse">Biinvertible</link> maps are <link href="erct-003F.xml" type="local" addr="erct-003F" title="Bijection">bijective</link></title>  <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-003H.agda" type="external">erct-003H.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>Any <link href="erct-000U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000U" title="Biinverse">biinvertible</link> map <tex>f \colon  A \to  B</tex> is a <link href="erct-003F.xml" type="local" addr="erct-003F" title="Bijection">bijection</link>.</p>
 
   
   <tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="false" numbered="true" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>808</anchor>  <taxon>Proof</taxon>    <date><year>2024</year> <month>2</month> <day>10</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors>  <parent>erct-003H</parent> </frontmatter> <mainmatter>
 <p>By <ref addr="erct-002W" href="erct-002W.xml" taxon="Lemma"/> and <ref addr="erct-002X" href="erct-002X.xml" taxon="Lemma"/>.</p>
</mainmatter> </tree>
 
</mainmatter> </tree><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>809</anchor> <rss>erct-003G.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Corollary</taxon> <addr>erct-003G</addr>  <route>erct-003G.xml</route> <date><year>2024</year> <month>2</month> <day>10</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>Being <link href="erct-003F.xml" type="local" addr="erct-003F" title="Bijection">bijective</link> is a <link href="erct-001I.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001I" title="Proposition">proposition</link></title>  <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-003G.agda" type="external">erct-003G.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>That a given map <tex>f \colon  A  \to  B</tex> is <link href="erct-003F.xml" type="local" addr="erct-003F" title="Bijection">bijective</link> is a <link href="erct-001I.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001I" title="Proposition">proposition</link>.</p>
 
   
   <tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="false" numbered="true" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>810</anchor>  <taxon>Proof</taxon>    <date><year>2024</year> <month>2</month> <day>10</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors>  <parent>erct-003G</parent> </frontmatter> <mainmatter>
 <p>By <ref addr="erct-002B" href="erct-002B.xml" taxon="Lemma"/>, <ref addr="erct-001U" href="erct-001U.xml" taxon="Lemma"/> via <ref addr="erct-001M" href="erct-001M.xml" taxon="Lemma"/>.</p>
</mainmatter> </tree>
 
</mainmatter> </tree><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>811</anchor> <rss>erct-003F.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Definition</taxon> <addr>erct-003F</addr>  <route>erct-003F.xml</route> <date><year>2024</year> <month>2</month> <day>10</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>Bijection</title>  <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-003F.agda" type="external">erct-003F.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>A function <tex>f \colon  A \to  B</tex> is called <em><strong>bijective</strong></em> when it is a <link href="erct-0029.xml" type="local" addr="erct-0029" title="Surjection">surjective</link> <link href="erct-001T.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001T" title="N-truncated map">propositional map</link>.</p></mainmatter> </tree><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>812</anchor> <rss>erct-003D.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Definition</taxon> <addr>erct-003D</addr>  <route>erct-003D.xml</route> <date><year>2024</year> <month>1</month> <day>4</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>Path object comprehension</title>  </frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>Let <tex>A</tex> be a <link href="erct-0010.xml" type="local" addr="erct-0010" title="Path object">path object</link>, and let <tex>B \colon  A \to   \mathsf {Prop}</tex> be a family of <link href="erct-001I.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001I" title="Proposition">propositions</link>. Then the dependent sum projection <tex>\pi _1 \colon \mathopen {} \left ( \mathchoice { \textstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( x:A \right ) \mathclose {} } }{ \textstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( x:A \right ) \mathclose {} } }{ \scriptstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( x:A \right ) \mathclose {} } }{ \scriptscriptstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( x:A \right ) \mathclose {} } } Bx \right ) \mathclose {} \to  A</tex> creates a <link href="erct-0010.xml" type="local" addr="erct-0010" title="Path object">path object</link> structure <tex>\mathopen {} \left \{ x:A \, \middle \vert \, Bx \right \} \mathclose {}</tex> on <tex>\mathchoice { \textstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( x:A \right ) \mathclose {} } }{ \textstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( x:A \right ) \mathclose {} } }{ \scriptstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( x:A \right ) \mathclose {} } }{ \scriptscriptstyle \sum _{ \mathopen {} \left ( x:A \right ) \mathclose {} } } Bx</tex> as follows:</p><ol><li>we have <tex>\mathopen {} \left ( x,u \right ) \mathclose {}   \cong _{ \mathopen {} \left \{ x:A \, \middle \vert \, Bx \right \} \mathclose {} }  \mathopen {} \left ( y,v \right ) \mathclose {}</tex> definitionally equal to <tex>x \cong _A y</tex>;</li>
 <li>the reflexivity datum <tex>1_{ \mathopen {} \left ( x,u \right ) \mathclose {} }</tex> is given by <tex>1_{ x }</tex> in <tex>A</tex>;</li>
 <li>univalence follows from univalence of <tex>A</tex> and the fact that <tex>B</tex> is valued in <link href="erct-001I.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001I" title="Proposition">propositions</link>.</li></ol></mainmatter> </tree><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>813</anchor> <rss>erct-002Z.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Corollary</taxon> <addr>erct-002Z</addr>  <route>erct-002Z.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>31</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title><link href="erct-003F.xml" type="local" addr="erct-003F" title="Bijection">Bijections</link> are <link href="erct-000U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000U" title="Biinverse">biinvertible</link></title>  <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-002Z.agda" type="external">erct-002Z.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>Any <link href="erct-003F.xml" type="local" addr="erct-003F" title="Bijection">bijection</link> <tex>f \colon  A \to  B</tex> is <link href="erct-000U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000U" title="Biinverse">biinvertible</link>.</p>
 
   
   <tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="false" numbered="true" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>814</anchor>  <taxon>Proof</taxon>    <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>31</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors>  <parent>erct-002Z</parent> </frontmatter> <mainmatter>
 <p>By <ref addr="erct-002Y" href="erct-002Y.xml" taxon="Lemma"/>, <link href="erct-003F.xml" type="local" addr="erct-003F" title="Bijection">bijections</link> are <link href="erct-001T.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001T" title="N-truncated map">contractible</link>; by <ref addr="erct-002H" href="erct-002H.xml" taxon="Corollary"/>, <link href="erct-003F.xml" type="local" addr="erct-003F" title="Bijection">bijections</link> are <link href="erct-001T.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001T" title="N-truncated map">contractible</link>.</p>
</mainmatter> </tree>
 
</mainmatter> </tree><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>815</anchor> <rss>erct-002S.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Corollary</taxon> <addr>erct-002S</addr>  <route>erct-002S.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>31</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>Being <link href="erct-000U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000U" title="Biinverse">biinvertible</link> is a <link href="erct-001I.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001I" title="Proposition">proposition</link></title>  <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-002S.agda" type="external">erct-002S.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>The type of <link href="erct-000U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000U" title="Biinverse">biinverses</link> of a given function <tex>f \colon  A \to  B</tex> is a <link href="erct-001I.xml" type="local" addr="erct-001I" title="Proposition">proposition</link>.</p>
 
   
   <tree expanded="true" show-heading="true" show-metadata="false" toc="false" numbered="true" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>816</anchor>  <taxon>Proof</taxon>    <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>31</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors>  <parent>erct-002S</parent> </frontmatter> <mainmatter>
 <link href="erct-002Q.xml" type="local" addr="erct-002Q" title="Sections of sections are unique">Sections of sections</link> and <link href="erct-002R.xml" type="local" addr="erct-002R" title="Retractions of retractions are unique">retractions of retractions</link> are unique.
</mainmatter> </tree>
 
</mainmatter> </tree><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>817</anchor> <rss>erct-000U.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Definition</taxon> <addr>erct-000U</addr>  <route>erct-000U.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>19</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>Biinverse</title>  <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-000U.agda" type="external">erct-000U.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>A <em><strong>biinverse</strong></em> to a function <tex>f \colon  A  \to  B</tex> is defined to be a pair of a <link href="erct-000Y.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000Y" title="Section-retraction pair">section</link> and a <link href="erct-000Y.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000Y" title="Section-retraction pair">retraction</link> to <tex>f</tex>. We will refer to a function <tex>f \colon  A \to  B</tex> equipped with a biinverse as a <em><strong>biinvertible function</strong></em>.</p></mainmatter> </tree><tree expanded="false" show-heading="true" show-metadata="true" toc="false" numbered="false" root="false"><frontmatter><anchor>818</anchor> <rss>erct-000V.rss.xml</rss> <taxon>Definition</taxon> <addr>erct-000V</addr>  <route>erct-000V.xml</route> <date><year>2023</year> <month>12</month> <day>19</day></date> <authors><author><link href="jonmsterling.xml" type="local" jonmsterling="addr">Jon Sterling</link></author> </authors> <title>Equivalence of types</title>  <meta name="source">
  
  
  <link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-000V.agda" type="external">erct-000V.agda</link>
</meta></frontmatter> <mainmatter><p>An <em><strong>equivalence</strong></em> from <tex>A</tex> to <tex>B</tex> is defined to be a function <tex>A  \to  B</tex> equipped with a  <link href="erct-000U.xml" type="local" addr="erct-000U" title="Biinverse">biinverse</link>.</p></mainmatter> </tree></related> <backlinks/> <references/></backmatter></tree>